Text.val: Pseudo group to include account with the same instrument-id

SQL_STMT_U.val:
select sum(round(q.qrd_value_asset,~4)) from qrap_data q inner join beleggingsinstrument b on b.be_volgnummer = q.qrd_instrument left outer join qrap_classification q1 on q1.be_id = q.qrd_instrument and q1.class_type = 'PO01' left outer join qrap_classification q2 on q2.be_id = q.qrd_instrument and q2.class_type = 'PO02'
where q.qrd_opdracht_id=~1 and decode(b.be_optietype, ' ', q1.class_code, 'CALL', q1.class_code, 'PUT', q1.class_code, 'FUT', q1.class_code, 6) = ~2 and decode(b.be_optietype, ' ', q2.class_code, 'CALL', q2.class_code, 'PUT', q2.class_code, 'FUT', q2.class_code, 69) = ~3
select sum(round(q.qrd_value_asset,~2)) from qrap_data q where q.qrd_opdracht_id=~1
select sum(q.qd_waarde_clv) from qrap_detail_port q where q.qd_opdracht_id=~1 and q.qd_asset_class = ~2 and q.qd_classificatie_1 = ~3
